left shift
N << i
2 << 1(Position)
010 << 1
100

Right Shift
N >> i
2 >> 1(Position)
010 >> 1
001

GetBit -- get the 3rd bit( position =2) of number n. (n= 0101)
1<<2
0001<<2
0010 & 0101
0001

SetBit
set the 2nd bit(position =1) of number n (n=0101)
1<<1
0001<<1
=0010 & 0101
= 0111->7


ClearBit
bit mask 1<<i
operation ANd and NOT
0001<<2= 0100
~(0100) --> 1011
1011 & 0101
=0001


updateBit
for 1 to 0
bit mask 1<<i
operation AND with NOT

for 0 to 1
bit mask 1<<i
operation OR


